---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Server-Side Tracking: Soluția Fără Cookies | ROA Marketing">
	<main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-20 max-w-6xl">
		<div class="text-center mb-20">
			<h1 class="text-7xl font-black mb-6 italic">Tracking <span class="text-cyan-400">Server-Side.</span></h1>
			<p class="text-2xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto italic">Ignoră AdBlocker-ele. Captează fiecare conversie. Dominația First-Party Data.</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
			<div class="space-y-8">
				<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-cyan-400">Acuratețe de 100%</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400">Datele sunt procesate pe propriul tău server înainte de a fi trimise către Google sau Meta. Niciun AdBlocker nu poate interveni.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="p-8 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Viteză de Încărcare</h3>
					<p class="text-slate-400">Eliminăm pixelii grei din browser-ul utilizatorului. Site-ul tău se încarcă instantaneu, crescând rata de conversie nativă.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- SVG DIAGRAM -->
			<div class="p-10 rounded-[40px] bg-slate-900 border border-cyan-500/20 shadow-[0_0_50px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
				<h4 class="text-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-10 text-slate-500">Arhitectura de Flux ROA 2026</h4>
				<svg viewBox="0 0 400 300" class="w-full h-auto text-white">
					<!-- Browser -->
					<rect x="20" y="100" width="80" height="50" rx="8" fill="#1e293b" stroke="#06b6d4" stroke-width="2" />
					<text x="60" y="130" text-anchor="middle" font-size="12" fill="white">Browser</text>
					
					<!-- Arrow 1 -->
					<path d="M100 125 L150 125" stroke="#06b6d4" stroke-width="2" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
					
					<!-- Server -->
					<rect x="160" y="80" width="100" height="90" rx="12" fill="#06b6d4" fill-opacity="0.1" stroke="#06b6d4" stroke-width="2" />
					<text x="210" y="120" text-anchor="middle" font-size="14" font-weight="bold" fill="#06b6d4">ROA Server</text>
					<text x="210" y="140" text-anchor="middle" font-size="10" fill="#64748b">GTM Server-Side</text>

					<!-- Arrow 2 -->
					<path d="M260 110 L310 70" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
					<path d="M260 125 L310 125" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />
					<path d="M260 140 L310 180" stroke="#64748b" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="4" marker-end="url(#arrow)" />

					<!-- Targets -->
					<text x="340" y="75" font-size="11" fill="#94a3b8">Google Ads</text>
					<text x="340" y="130" font-size="11" fill="#94a3b8">Meta API</text>
					<text x="340" y="185" font-size="11" fill="#94a3b8">TikTok CAPI</text>

					<defs>
						<marker id="arrow" markerWidth="10" markerHeight="10" refX="0" refY="3" orient="auto" markerUnits="strokeWidth">
							<path d="M0,0 L0,6 L9,3 z" fill="#06b6d4" />
						</marker>
					</defs>
				</svg>
			</div>
		</div>

		<section class="mt-32 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Nu mai pierde date. Nu mai pierde bani.</h2>
			<a href="#contact" class="inline-block px-12 py-6 bg-white text-black font-black text-2xl rounded-3xl hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-all">Implementează Acum</a>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
